# ── Required (set in Vercel dashboard) ────────────────────────────────
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY     - OpenRouter API key
# ASSISTANT_MODELS       - Comma-separated model IDs (e.g. deepseek/...,minimax/...)
# ASSISTANT_SYSTEM_PROMPT - Full system prompt for the AI agent

# ── Optional ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ASSISTANT_API_URL       - API endpoint (default: OpenRouter)
# ASSISTANT_REASONING     - Enable reasoning (default: true)
# ASSISTANT_REASONING_EFFORT - high / xhigh (default: high)
# ASSISTANT_MAX_TOKENS    - Max response tokens (default: 512)
# ASSISTANT_TEMPERATURE   - Temperature (default: 0.7)
# ASSISTANT_REFERER_URL   - HTTP-Referer header
# ASSISTANT_SITE_TITLE    - X-Title header
